---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="CLI Commands">
  <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">
    <a href="/docs" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Docs</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span class="text-white">CLI Commands</span>
  </nav>

  <div class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">CLI Commands</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">
      Complete reference for all Aura OS command-line interface commands.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6" id="quick-reference">Quick Reference</h2>
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">aura</span> <span class="text-green-400">setup</span>            <span class="text-zinc-500"># Initialize wallet</span></div>
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">aura</span> <span class="text-green-400">chat</span> <span class="text-yellow-400">"message"</span>   <span class="text-zinc-500"># Send AI command</span></div>
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">aura</span> <span class="text-green-400">status</span>          <span class="text-zinc-500"># Check configuration</span></div>
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">aura</span> <span class="text-green-400">help</span>            <span class="text-zinc-500"># Show help</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="setup">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <code class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 rounded-lg font-mono text-lg">aura setup</code>
    </div>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Initialize Aura OS by securely storing your wallet's private key. The key is encrypted using AES-256 
      encryption and stored locally on your device.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Interactive Prompts</h3>
    <div class="terminal mb-6">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-2">
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura setup</span></div>
        <div class="text-blue-400 mt-2">Welcome to Aura OS - AI Agent Manager</div>
        <div class="text-zinc-400">? Enter your private key (will be encrypted locally): ********</div>
        <div class="text-zinc-400">? Set Master Password to protect your wallet: ********</div>
        <div class="text-green-400 mt-2">✓ Setup complete! Your private key is protected by AES-256.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-card p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500 bg-blue-500/5">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-blue-400 text-lg">💡</span>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Tip</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-1">
            Your master password is used to decrypt your private key when executing transactions. 
            Choose a strong password and store it securely.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="chat">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <code class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 rounded-lg font-mono text-lg">aura chat "message"</code>
    </div>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Send a natural language command to Aura's AI interpreter. The AI parses your intent and 
      validates it against supported Web3 actions.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Arguments</h3>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
      <table class="w-full text-left text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
            <th class="py-2 px-3 text-zinc-400">Argument</th>
            <th class="py-2 px-3 text-zinc-400">Required</th>
            <th class="py-2 px-3 text-zinc-400">Description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
            <td class="py-2 px-3"><code class="text-yellow-400">message</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 px-3 text-green-400">Yes</td>
            <td class="py-2 px-3 text-zinc-300">Your command in natural language</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Examples</h3>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
          <span class="ml-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">Check Balance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
          <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura chat</span> <span class="text-yellow-400">"Check my ETH balance"</span></div>
          <div class="text-zinc-500 mt-2">Aura is thinking...</div>
          <div class="text-green-400">✓ Valid command: CHECK_BALANCE</div>
          <div class="text-cyan-400">  Token: ETH</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
          <span class="ml-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">Send Token</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
          <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura chat</span> <span class="text-yellow-400">"Send 0.5 ETH to 0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc454e4438f44e"</span></div>
          <div class="text-zinc-500 mt-2">Aura is thinking...</div>
          <div class="text-green-400">✓ Valid command: SEND_TOKEN</div>
          <div class="text-cyan-400">  Token: ETH</div>
          <div class="text-cyan-400">  Amount: 0.5</div>
          <div class="text-cyan-400">  Target: 0x742d35Cc...</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
          <span class="ml-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">Vietnamese (Tiếng Việt)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
          <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura chat</span> <span class="text-yellow-400">"Kiểm tra số dư ETH của tôi"</span></div>
          <div class="text-zinc-500 mt-2">Aura is thinking...</div>
          <div class="text-green-400">✓ Valid command: CHECK_BALANCE</div>
          <div class="text-cyan-400">  Token: ETH</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
          <span class="ml-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">Rejected (Non-Web3)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
          <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura chat</span> <span class="text-yellow-400">"How do I cook rice?"</span></div>
          <div class="text-zinc-500 mt-2">Aura is thinking...</div>
          <div class="text-red-400">❌ Rejected: Aura OS only supports Web3 tasks. I cannot help you cook.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="status">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <code class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 rounded-lg font-mono text-lg">aura status</code>
    </div>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Check the current configuration status of Aura OS, including wallet setup and API key configuration.
    </p>

    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura status</span></div>
        <div class="text-blue-400 mt-2">⚡ Aura OS Status</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">  ✓ Wallet configured</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">  ✓ Vault encrypted (AES-256)</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">  ✓ OpenAI API key configured</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="actions">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Supported Actions</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The AI Interpreter recognizes these actions from your natural language commands:
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="glass-card p-5">
        <code class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 rounded text-sm">CHECK_BALANCE</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-3">Query token balance for connected wallet</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-2">
          <strong>Triggers:</strong> "check", "balance", "how much"
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card p-5">
        <code class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 rounded text-sm">SEND_TOKEN</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-3">Transfer tokens to another address</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-2">
          <strong>Triggers:</strong> "send", "transfer", "gửi"
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card p-5">
        <code class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 rounded text-sm">SWAP_TOKEN</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-3">Swap between supported tokens</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-2">
          <strong>Triggers:</strong> "swap", "exchange", "convert"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-zinc-500">
      <strong class="text-zinc-400">Supported tokens:</strong> ETH, SUI, USDT, USDC
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="errors">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Error Handling</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Aura OS provides clear error messages when something goes wrong:
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="glass-card p-4 border-l-4 border-red-500">
        <code class="text-red-400 text-sm font-mono">❌ Error: Message is required</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-2">You called <code>aura chat</code> without a message. Add your command in quotes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
        <code class="text-yellow-400 text-sm font-mono">⚠ Wallet not configured</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-2">Run <code>aura setup</code> first to configure your wallet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
        <code class="text-yellow-400 text-sm font-mono">⚠ OpenAI API key not found</code>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-2">Set <code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code> in your <code>.env</code> file.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Next Steps</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="/docs/vault" class="bento-card group block">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">
          🔐 Secure Vault
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Learn how your keys are encrypted and stored.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/ai-interpreter" class="bento-card group block">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">
          🧠 AI Interpreter
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Understand how commands are parsed.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
